/* ==========================================
   EMMA TALK TOPICS — COMMON PHASE, LEVEL 1
   phase === "common" && friendshipLevel === 1

   CHARACTER: Emma Walsh, Waitress at Ruby's Diner
   → Competent, always tired, professional distance.
   → Not a bad person, just busy.
   → Tone: Short, dry, direct.

   COMMON L1 TONE:
   → Player has no job, just dropped by.
   → Like an old coworker — talks about work casually.
   → CRITICAL: No orders, no tables, no menus. Just chatting.

   CONTEXTS:
   dinerRubys_common_morning
   dinerRubys_common_afternoon
   dinerRubys_common_evening
========================================== */

