<<dialog "player">>Is he checking his watch or something?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress1">>I think the dog is the one with the schedule. The guy's just getting dragged along. _(smiles faintly)_<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Can't argue with a dog on a mission.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress1">>Now they're gonna turn the corner and disappear... and yep, right on cue.<</dialog>`,
